Plans for 0.5.0
===============

  * General
      - Use "." as decimal for time
      - Move variables from application and project to delegates?
      - Raise exceptions instead of returning None or False
      - Get rid of logger
      - Use class variables and refer to them as self.var?
          - gaupol.base.files
      - never use plural names in directory and file names???
      - Update copyright notices to -2006
      - string.Template for preview command?
      - Framerate conversion available for time-based subs
      - Put a .pot file in the trunk
      - Mime-type registration?
      - Remove --no-translation option?
      - C:\Program Files\VideoLAN\vlc\vlc.exe + MPlayer

  * setup.py / setup.cfg
      - Don't install any testing
      - python 2.5 uninstall?
      - Remove setup.cfg?
      - setup.py: destination vs. configure (Arch)
         - setup.py install --prefix=/usr --root=tmp/pkg
         - Add a destdir option to install
         - finalize_options: x = os.path.join(destdir, x)
         - paths.py: if destdir: ...
      - Use intltool-merge for gaupol.desktop file translations?
          - See alacarte source code
      - clean command
      - Do setup.py install options work?
          --prefix           OK
          --exec-prefix
          --home
          --install-base
          --install-platbase
          --root
          --install-purelib
          --install-lib
          --install-scripts
          --install-data

  * base
      - Gaupol hangs if video player not closed before exit
      - Use action grouping in replace_both_texts(...)
      - Add exception handling for preview command being a blank string
      - FileOpenDelegate._sort_data: return amount of sorts made

  * gtk
      - No need to check if translator-credits is translated
      - Unlimited undo by default?
      - UIM name: /ui/menubar/edit/edit
      - Spell-check dialog mnemonics: Join _Back, Join _Forward
      - Redirect/copy sys.stdout to output window?
      - Adjust Durations dialog: Target
      - Menu item locations:
          - Framerate
          - Select Video
          - Headers
      - Remove Unselect All menu item?

  New Features:
